937
01:40:35,634 --> 01:40:39,718
So about 10% of the revenue that is credit card-based, not cash.

938
01:40:41,280 --> 01:40:43,203
Now goes to merchant processing as opposed to 25%.

939
01:40:44,325 --> 01:40:50,995
So these numbers I budgeted for are based on the averages and those averages including the cost of heartland.

940
01:40:51,596 --> 01:40:53,639
So they should be lower than what I've.

941
01:40:54,844 --> 01:40:59,388
predicted, given that we don't have a huge uptick in people parking at the meters.

