01:40:59,989 --> 01:41:08,556
I'm working with G-Techno to switch them from Heartland to AMG as well for more cost savings there with our credit card processing fees.

943
01:41:08,936 --> 01:41:11,538
In addition to that, switching to AMG allowed our

944
01:41:12,600 --> 01:41:17,145
