01:42:20,850 --> 01:42:24,932
Supplies, clothing budget was higher than we've needed the last couple of years.

952
01:42:25,352 --> 01:42:31,114
A couple of the other line items were higher than we really used, so we made some small cuts there.

953
01:42:33,355 --> 01:42:35,536
I say small, but it was actually pretty substantial.

954
01:42:38,097 --> 01:42:38,557
It looks like 12.

