01:43:25,877 --> 01:43:36,064
And I've had a few, I've had a few issues with them myself where they have tried to invoice me for things that specifically they tried to invoice me to switch to AMG.

961
01:43:37,546 --> 01:43:40,828
And when I gave them some pushback, they were like, okay, fine, just you won't have to take.

962
01:43:40,888 --> 01:43:42,930
So, so I have a feeling that they, they,

