One deputy chief and six police officers, yes.

1527
02:26:10,690 --> 02:26:10,910
Great.

1528
02:26:11,070 --> 02:26:11,370
Okay.

1529
02:26:11,650 --> 02:26:12,971
Six patrol deputy chief.

1530
02:26:13,391 --> 02:26:13,571
Yes.

1531
02:26:13,691 --> 02:26:14,492
Funded at a dollar.

1532
02:26:16,579 --> 02:26:17,499
effective staffing is 105.

1533
02:26:17,539 --> 02:26:19,360
What's that?

1534
02:26:19,600 --> 02:26:22,281
The effective staffing is 105 uniformed officers.

1535
02:26:22,962 --> 02:26:24,703
We're funded, yeah.

1536
02:26:24,843 --> 02:26:25,143
Okay.

1537
02:26:25,383 --> 02:26:25,663
All right.

1538
02:26:25,703 --> 02:26:28,544
That's the whole department, 105, not just uniformed officers.

1539
