As a council, we'd vote on the budget appropriation, the stabilization fund appropriation and the free cash transfer.

1787
02:45:04,208 --> 02:45:15,094
That would be on June 9th when the budget is presented and if the mayor provides us an appropriation for the free cash and the stabilization fund.

1788
02:45:16,975 --> 02:45:17,496
Yes, thank you.

1789
02:45:17,896 --> 02:45:18,216
Thank you.

1790
