So just to introduce myself.

1822
02:47:04,130 --> 02:47:07,115
My name is Noel Velez, the director of finance for Memphis Public Schools.

1823
02:47:08,197 --> 02:47:18,633
And as the superintendent was talking about earlier, this was great, tremendous work by principals, directors, and our admin assistants who scheduled over 60 meetings.

1824
02:47:19,534 --> 02:47:28,139
between October to March to try to get what we felt was not just an accurate number, but making sure that everyone felt that the students were put first.

1825
02:47:28,519 --> 02:47:31,581
And I believe that this budget represents that, where we put students first.

1826
02:47:32,281 --> 02:47:42,747
