02:47:50,894 --> 02:47:57,396
So, one of the first things we do in our budget development cycle is to look at enrollment.

1830
02:47:57,636 --> 02:48:10,822
October 1 is a benchmark enrollment number for us and that's also used by the Department of Education to create the foundation budget.

1831
02:48:10,902 --> 02:48:16,504
So, it's an important number and you could see that we're trending

1832
