down a little bit and not precipitously but we have about 100 fewer students projected for next school year versus October of 2024.

1833
02:48:31,949 --> 02:48:46,872
We do have larger than, slightly larger than average class sizes moving through the middle schools right now and eventually they'll be at the high school

1834
02:48:49,164 --> 02:48:52,928
but overall slightly trending down right now.

