I'm curious as to what you guys see as the impact to students and to families if the gap isn't plucked.

2045
03:18:35,298 --> 03:18:36,159
what's on the docket.

2046
03:18:38,240 --> 03:18:39,241
Can I answer, can I start?

2047
03:18:39,261 --> 03:18:39,381
Sure.

2048
03:18:39,581 --> 03:18:39,861
Yeah.

