2723
04:17:37,070 --> 04:17:39,932
It's Mass General Law Chapter 44, Section 31D.

2724
04:17:39,972 --> 04:17:45,675
It talks about snow and ice removal and emergency expenditures and the reporting requirements under that statute.

2725
04:17:45,735 --> 04:17:56,701
It specifically says that the appropriation for such purposes in any said fiscal year must effectively equal or exceed the appropriation for said purposes in the prior fiscal year.

2726
04:17:57,262 --> 04:18:00,764
So cities and towns intentionally do not increase this line.

2727
04:18:02,044 --> 04:18:05,886
for the purpose of not finding themselves in a situation where they have a surplus.

2728
